Hello Driver! Welcome to world of Pickup Craze. Get ready for a crazy adventure. The road ahead is tricky. All you have to do is stay alive. Do you have what it takes?

Make sure you collect coins to unlock new vehicles. Ohhh and fuels are limited. Do not forget to refill on the road.
Watch out for bridge. They can be very tricky. You can easily get stuck or worse, crash
Finishing line represents the end of this level. Cross them to go to next level.
Oops looks like you have reached the moving bridge. Wait for it to get close before getting on or you might meet death soon.
